Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:15.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:27.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.47,0:00:37.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:45.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:52.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:57.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:00.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:04.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:08.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:11.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:15.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.37,0:01:19.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To prepare for Gel Shocker's all-out attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:27.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Leech Chameleon is working to\Nrevive their old monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:32.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi learned of their\Nplan and infiltrated their base,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:36.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but he fell into Leech Chameleon's trap and was\Nleft unable to transform into Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:02.64,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx110\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,160.389)}Gel Shocker Destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:02.64,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,720.389)}The Leader's End!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten the second Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... save the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Hurry, to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This base will explode in five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Hongo. Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the time bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it... a ticking sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thirty seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Head Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, I've turned it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Leech Chameleon...\NWhere is General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Riders One and Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come out!\N- We have Leech Chameleon hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:47.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'll release the prisoners we were\Nusing for Gel Shocker experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You release Leech Chameleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:00.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Come to the Hall of Monsters\Nat Pal Pal Amusement Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:03.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning at 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:12.40,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H365C02&\3c&HC5EAF3&}Pal Pal Amusement Park
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Hall of Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't have picked\Na more appropriate place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dawn soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're skilled likenesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 4:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We've brought Leech Chameleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:58.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&HC1EFFD&}Welcome, \NKamen Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You've finally arrived... Hongo\NTakeshi... Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'm right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Leech Chameleon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was throwing my voice with ventriloquism!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All to lure you this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Leech Chameleon, have brought\Nall the monsters back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools... watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness Leech Chameleon's true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've underestimated us, General Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We know Gel Shocker commanders-in-chief\Nare always monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We walked into your trap\Nto expose your true face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hongo! Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tail the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You chase General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My role has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose to die in glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riders... listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who laughs last...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who laughs last is Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to our
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,great leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's commanders were\Nall brave in their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This leaves only their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Taki tracked them back successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:32.46,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't chase them too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's leader\Nwill be there this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave their leader to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine why they'd\Nmeet their leader here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When did they disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you've outlived your usefulness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like it, Taki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Our General Black was\Nan excellent leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He set one last trap,\Nknowing it would kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One last trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd lure Hongo Takeshi and\NIchimonji Hayato to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then let us kill them in front\Nof you and the Rider Kid Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting to\Nhear from you all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Members of the Rider Kid Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Gel Shocker leader's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,Your organization is hereby dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never dissolve as\Nlong as you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:46.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,Today, Gel Shocker will mount\Na massive attack on Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:50.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,Japan will be ours by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider will stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:58.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,You can see for yourselves\Nhow your Riders die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How our Riders die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:04.99,Italics,,0,0,0,,We'll escort you all to the\Ntheir execution grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Hongo and Ichimonji finish you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to take you to the\NRiders' execution grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,Taki, can you hear me? Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki here. \NThe bridge over Lake Hamana looks suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:29.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo. It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your protestations fall on deaf ears, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our computer can produce a\Nvoice identical to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Hongo Takeshi can catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will execute them in the\NJapan Gel Shocker headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,located beneath Lake Hamana\Nin the center of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place Taki mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hongo Takeshi! Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker's leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:16.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's time for Gel Shocker's\Nfinal show of hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghosts out of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Transform!\N- Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.75,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:49.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:53.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:57.04,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.28,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.29,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:06.68,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:11.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.82,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:29.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.18,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.77,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:50.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself at last, Leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeating you will restore\Npeace to our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Foolish Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Taki!\N- Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go save your allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Riders, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig deep and stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we die now,\Nthis will all be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Riders, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Riders!\N- Hang in there, Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader... there's nowhere to run now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon your quest for world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us who you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... you've finally seen my true face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what their leader really was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've brought about\Nthe end of Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll make sure you join us in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A dramatic end for Gel Shocker's leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Their leader's real brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Their base blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it took the Riders with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.00,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H3B3CFF&\3c&HAABCC1&}Tokyo International Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take care of yourself out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to head out\Nwithout seeing the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The days have been long and hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With peace restored, they'll\Nfeel like good memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, come see us again, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure the Rider Kid\NCorps keeps going strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back and see us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do the rest on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:50.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:53.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and their terrifying leader had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:59.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Riders, Hongo\NTakeshi and Ichimonji Hayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,had survived their deathmatch\Nagainst Gel Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:02.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and their long trial had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.05,0:23:07.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was time for peace to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.69,Cont,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\fs155\blur.8\pos(480,318)}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:19.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:22.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:26.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:30.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:41.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:46.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:52.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker Destroyed!\NThe Leader's End!!